//in cqlsh 

CREATE KEYSPACE queries WITH replication = {'class': 'SimpleStrategy', 'replication_factor' : 2};
USE queries;

CREATE TABLE q1(
sqldate int,
language text,
country text,
numarticles int,
numevents int,
PRIMARY KEY (sqldate, language, country));
CREATE TABLE q2(
country text,
globaleventid int,
year text,
month text,
day text,
numarticles int,
PRIMARY KEY ((country,globaleventid,year,month,day)));

val  df_explode_themes = troi_req.withColumn("V2Themes", split($"V2Themes", ";")) 
                        .select($"GLOBALEVENTID", explode($"V2Themes").as("SplittedThemes"))
val  df_explode_locations = troi_req.withColumn("V2Locations", split($"V2Locations", ";"))
                         .select($"GLOBALEVENTID", explode($"V2Locations").as("SplittedLocations"))
val  df_explode_persons = troi_req.withColumn("V2Persons", split($"V2Persons", ";"))       
                        .select($"GLOBALEVENTID", explode($"V2Persons").as("SplittedPersons"))
